    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >畅玩老派清版射击游戏，夺回宇宙！</h2><br><br>《RedRaptor》是一款纵向清版射击游戏，其灵感源自上世纪九十年代的同类经典之作：你将在该游戏中发射升空，体验复古街机游戏的乐趣！扮演一位执行拦截任务的王牌飞行员，迎击一个已经消灭几乎所有盟军的未知威胁。如果你想活下来并打败敌人，就得一路升级你的飞船并将你的技能发挥到极限！<br><br>当蜂拥而至的敌船和环境风险欲致你于死命时，飞向天空，进入行星低轨，前往敌方太空站，造访小行星带等等。管理你的护盾并留意你的生命值 ！每玩一局，你都能对己方飞船的统计数据进行永久性升级，从武器级别到激光甚至僚机飞行员。你能征服 5 个弹幕射击关卡并探索深渊深处隐藏的秘密吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404210/extras/c55cf6829313fd769b5c6b4a26aeaae4.poster.avif?t=1720816984\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404210/extras/c55cf6829313fd769b5c6b4a26aeaae4.webm?t=1720816984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404210/extras/c55cf6829313fd769b5c6b4a26aeaae4.mp4?t=1720816984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>游戏特点：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>玩转 5 个独特的弹幕射击关卡！<br></li><li>为你的飞船赢得永久升级。<br></li><li>体验从同类经典游戏汲取灵感的纵向卷轴风格，在蜂拥而至的敌军中杀开一条血路。<br></li><li>管理护盾和武器，新增僚机飞行员等等！<br></li><li>挑战在线排行榜！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404210/extras/dfc2aeabb68adc26be3ce30c0fe9b96a.poster.avif?t=1720816984\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404210/extras/dfc2aeabb68adc26be3ce30c0fe9b96a.webm?t=1720816984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404210/extras/dfc2aeabb68adc26be3ce30c0fe9b96a.mp4?t=1720816984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
